review_blob: The aromas and impressions are floral above all. Floral with a hunch of grass. It has a nice smell of apricots. Goes with almost everything that is steaked or grilled.
This has been my favourite beer for about a year now. Taste of yeast, citrus and banana. It has a nice white head.
I found this one att Systembolaget. It doesent taste like the other wheats on the shelves. I liked the burnt taste and it made me feel sumry.
